Statistics for variable 4

Statistics for variable 4

calcP_EX(years = 1990:2020, var = FALSE)

Arguments

years
years to calculate
var
If true, return only variable 4. If false, return intermediate statistics needed for variable 4

Value

if var = FALSE, necessary calculations for Variable 4 for selected years if var = TRUE, returns values for Variable 4 for selected years

Examples

calcP_EX(var = TRUE)
